This was the ﬁrst preliminary report of the constituents of
biological activities. The oils were composed mostly of fatty acids, but the Ilha do Cardoso population

analyzed presented differences in their essential oil contents, this might be an indication of different

prove if these differences are not only due to environmental factors. Concerning the biological activities
